Japan offers 1 . 2 trln yen of six - month T - bills . The Ministry of Finance said on Thursday it was offering 1 . 2 trillion yen worth of six - month Treasury bills ( T - bills ) through a price competitive auction . The auction will close at 0300 GMT and the results will be announced at 0530 GMT . The issue date will be September 10 and maturity date will be March 10 , 1997 . 
